{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhounan-011__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhounan-011", "source_id": "guofeng-zhounan-011__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "poem", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·周南·011.1", "text_original": "麟之趾，振振公子，于嗟麟兮。\n麟之定，振振公姓，于嗟麟兮。\n麟之角，振振公族，于嗟麟兮。", "text_normalized": "麟之趾，振振公子，于嗟麟兮。\n麟之定，振振公姓，于嗟麟兮。\n麟之角，振振公族，于嗟麟兮。", "notes": "麟之趾 Chinese poem 1."}
